Taylor Swift is an iconic name in the Hollywood's Top Artists who is known for writing songs that mostly seem to relate with many people around the globe. 
She's known as an **American SweetHeart** and has been a proud receipient of many awards, including the prestigious Grammy Awards and others.

To know more about [Taylor Swift](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Taylor_Swift), do read the article on Wikipedia and get ready to be amazed and inspired.
